That said, it's very odd to me that the inconsistency occurred. ti.hostname is stored using socket.fqdn(), but in your screenshot it appears to be only the hostname part.  I suppose this could be possible if (1) the celery worker is using a different (older) version of airflow or (2) the TI is re-run where the original run date was before the pr change; or (3) there are some EMC setting oddity.

